                    <ab>Igitur nos prenominatus <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/3042">secundus
                            Robbertus</persName> divina ordinante clementia Capuanorum <rs
                            key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>. Notum fieri volumus omnibus filiis sancte
                        aecclesie et nostris fidelibus, quoniam ob salutem et remedium animarum
                        quondam <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosorum</rs>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principum</rs> parentum antecessorum nostrorum, et ob
                        statum nostri principatus, consilio quoque et <rs key="#Intercessory"
                            >interventu</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory #fidelisOf" ref="#people/4267">Raynaldi
                            cognomento Musca</persName> nostri karissimi baronis et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #fidelisOf" ref="#people/4269">Octonis Malivicini
                        </persName>atque <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer #fidelisOf"
                            ref="#people/3035">Odoaldi</persName> nostri <rs
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer">camerarii</rs> et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #fidelisOf" ref="#people/4268">Cansolini</persName>,
                        nec non aliorum nostrorum dilectorum <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelium</rs> in
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/3046">Sancti Angeli quod
                            dicitur in Formis</orgName> in quo domnus <persName
                            key="#Prevosts #Personal_rank" ref="#people/3043">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs> ac Deo dignus <rs key="#Prevosts"
                            >prepositus</rs> esse videtur, per hoc videlicet principale scriptum in
                        perpetuum damus et tradendo confirmamus. Hoc est integram unam <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >petiam</rs> de terra que est prope dextructam <rs key="#Churches"
                            >aecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3032">Sancti Martini qui
                            dicitur ad Lavem</orgName>, et habet hos <rs key="#Fines">fines</rs>
                        ipsa petia de terra: a parte orientis est finis terra ecclesie Sancti
                        Iacobi; a parte septemtrionis est finis terra heredum quondam Iohannis
                        iaconi Petri: a parte occidentis est finis terra heredum quondam Iohannis
                        Falconis et finis terra predicte aecclesie Sancti Iacobi; a parte meridie
                        est finis via publica. Hanc autem predictam petia terre per predictos fines
                        una cum omnibus inferioribus ac superioribus suis et cum <rs key="#Roads"
                            >via</rs> sua ibidem intrandi et exeundi atque cum omnibus suis
                        pertinentiis, nos memoratus secundus Robbertus Dei gratia Capuanorum
                        princeps, damus, tradimus, concedimus, ac confirmamus per hoc videlicet
                        principale scriptum in perpetuum, in predicto monasterio Sancti Angeli qui
                        dicitur in Formis, ad possessionem et potestatem atque dominationem iam
                        dicti monasterii Sancti Angeli et prenominati domni Petri venerabilis
                        prepositi et de eiusdem monasterii custodibus atque rectoribus, faciendi
                        exinde quicquid eis placuerit. Rursum quoque nos prenominatus secundus
                        Robbertus Dei gratia Capuanorum princeps per interventum prescriptorum
                        videlicet Rainaldi cognomento Musca et Octonis cognomento Malusvicinus et
                        aliorum suprascriptorum nostrorum fidelium in predicto monasterio Sancti
                        Angeli qui dicitur in Formis, in quo domnus Petrus venerabilis prepositus
                        preest, per hoc videlicet principale scriptum in perpetuum damus, tradimus,
                        concedimus ac confirmamus hos subscriptos <rs key="#Coloni/tenants"
                            >homines</rs> cum <rs key="#childOf">filiis, filiabus</rs> atque <rs
                            key="#heirTo">heredibus </rs>eorum, et <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >cum omnibus rebus et possessionibus eorum</rs>, ut ipsi, et filii et
                        filie atque heredes eorum faciant et persolvant semper in predicto
                        monasterio Sancti Angeli et iam dicto domno Petro venerabili preposito, et
                        ad eiusdem monasterii custodibus atque rectoribus <rs
                            key="#Public_exactions">quicquid nobis nostre publici parte facere aut
                            persolvere debent aut debuerint</rs>. Nomina quorum hec sunt: <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Iohannes Petri Biti">Iohannes
                                cognomento Petri Biti</name></persName>, et <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf #siblingOf"><name ref="Lando Petri Biti"
                                >Lando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs> eius qui fuerunt <rs key="#childOf"
                            >filii</rs>
                        <persName><name ref="Petrus Bitus">Petri Biti</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Petrus Bactalia">Petrus
                                Battalia</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf #siblingOf"><name ref="Vitus Bactalia"
                                >Vitus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs> eius <rs key="#childOf">fili</rs> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Bactalia">Bactalia</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannes</name></persName> et <persName key="#Deacons #childOf"><name
                                ref="Maio">Maio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Deacons">diaconus</rs>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs> quondam <persName key="#Priests"><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Priests">presbiteri</rs>; <persName key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"
                                ><name ref="Maio">Maio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <persName><name ref="Grimoaldus"
                                >Grimoaldi</name></persName>; <rs key="#childOf">filie</rs> quondam,
                            <persName key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohannes</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Rotius"
                            >Rutus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs> quondam <persName><name ref="Stadius Rotii"
                                >Stadii Ruti</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Desua">Desua</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filia</rs> quondam <persName><name ref="Temarius"
                                >Temari</name></persName>; <persName key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"
                                ><name ref="Pandulfus">Pandulfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <rs key="#Priests">presbyteri</rs>
                        <persName key="#Priests"><name ref="Pandulfus">Pandulfi</name></persName>;
                            <persName key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Stadia"
                                >Stadia</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filia</rs> quondam <persName><name ref="Robertus"
                                >Robberti</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Robertus"
                            >Robbertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <persName><name ref="Rotius"
                                >Rutii</name></persName>; <persName key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"
                                ><name ref="Gentilis">Gentilis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes Landi Dardani">Iohannis Landi
                            Dardani</name></persName>; <persName key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"
                                ><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Petrus Landi Dardani">Petri Landi Dardani</name></persName>;
                            <persName key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Stabilis"
                                >Stabilis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <persName><name ref="Sabatinus"
                                >Sabatini</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Sabatinus"
                            >Sabbatinus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <persName><name ref="Maio Fayda"
                                >Maionis Fayde</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <persName><name ref="Lando"
                                >Landonis</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Iohannes"
                            >Iohannes</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Lando Mariae Sassi">Landonis Marie Sassi;</name></persName>
                        <persName key="#Coloni/tenants #childOf"><name ref="Landulfus"
                                >Landulfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <persName><name ref="Maria Dominici"
                                >Marie Dominici</name></persName> * * * Homines isti sunt
                        habitatores in loco <placeName key="#Coloni/tenants" ref="#places/4528"
                            >Sarzano</placeName>. Remota omni inquietudine, contrarietate vel
                        molestia omnium principum successorum nostrorum vel vice principum, comitum
                        vel vice comitum, iudicum, sculdahorum, castaldeorum aliorumque omnium
                        mortalium personarum. Quod si quis huius nostre concessionis atque
                        confirmationis pagine contemptor aut violator extiterit, aut contra hoc
                        principale scriptum hagere temptaverit, <rs key="#Penalty">quinquaginta
                            libras auri purissimi </rs>persolvat: medietatem prenominato monasterio
                        Sancti Angeli et iam dicto domno Petro venerabili preposito et eiusdem
                        monasterii custodibus atque rectoribus, et medietatem nostro sacro palatio.
                        Solutaque pena librarum auri, hoc principale scriptum firmum permaneat in
                        perpetuum. Ut autem firmius credatur et diligentius ab omnibus observetur,
                        manu propria subscribens illud corroboravimus, et nostri sigilli illud
                        insigniri iussimus. (M) Ex iussione prephate potestatis, scripsi ego
                            <persName key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/3037">Philippus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">palatinus iudex</rs>, in anno dominicae incarnationis
                        millesimo centesimo vicesimo nono, et secundo anno principatus prescripti
                        domni secundi Robberti <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis"
                            >gloriosissimi</rs> principis Capue. Datum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/173">Capue</placeName> in mense * * * * per indictionem
                        VIIa</ab>
                </div>
